   inherit kde-v3
   require flex kdeaccessibility-v3 kdemultimedia-v3 libXScrnSaver
  optional openssl    --with-ssl               --without-ssl          for SSL support
  optional cyrus-sasl --with-sasl              --without-sasl         enable support for authentication through cyrus-sasl
  optional gnokii     --with-gnokii            --without-gnokii       for mobile phone support
  optional gpgme      --with-gpgme-prefix=/usr --without-gpgme-prefix for GPG support
  switch              --enable-exchange        --disable-exchange     for Microsoft Exchange 2000 support
  category utility/office
  homepage http://www.kde.org
# gpgme a mandatory requirement?

  estimate 11200
      desc 'Personal information management apps
kdepim contains:
kab2     another design for the KDE addressbook
ldif     a parser for LDIF, the LDAP Information Interchange Format
libdif   dito, one of them is superfluous
libical  a basic iCalendar protocol implementation, see RFCs 2245,2246
libimap  IMAP handling
libkcal  C++ api for the iCalendar and vCalendar formats
librmm   an Internet mail message parser (RFC 822 -> Class hierarchy)
vCard    a vCard 3.0 (virtual business card) parser
kgantt   lib to display and manage Gantt diagrams'
